  "id": "RAW_2dfc1ae4",
  "title": "1.8B！腾讯开源新模型，1GB 内存手机离线跑，媲美 Qwen3-235B",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==&mid=2652794837&idx=2&sn=d3a74017bf90d65118266b9b55272253",
  "date": "2025-12-30 12:31:00",
