  "siteName": "智东西",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=05095835&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRwIqk5ASvCHickKf4OBXickuLPreLahcMElm7mbrN8oyxTM4iczUU6gdePA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">能翻译33语种+5方言，医学术语/粤语翻译实测“能打”。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">王涵</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">冰倩</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">智东西12月30日报道，刚刚，腾讯混元开源</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">翻译模型1.5版本</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，共包含两个模型：</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Tencent-HY-MT1.5-1.8B和Tencent-HY-MT1.5-7B</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，支持</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">33个</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">语种互译以及</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">5种</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">民汉/方言，除了中文、英语、日语等常见语种，也包含捷克语、马拉地语、爱沙尼亚语、冰岛语等小语种。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.507\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b912a85c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRw7PlLdTiaQxfeBrJ3QcbkjVvNiaUFGSXoZVl05YZBxhxW1ZjE1WaPc4icQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲Tencent-HY-MT1.5-1.8B开源（来源：Hugging Face）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.558\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15251a06&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRwt5sC8tvTiaUXlomic6FicZdiaZvPtYyj1icB0tyJudk5h5h4hichicWD6vafg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲Tencent-HY-MT1.5-7B开源（来源：Hugging Face）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">HY-MT1.5-1.8B主要面向</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">手机等消费级设备场景</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，支持端侧直接部署和离线实时翻译，仅需</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">1GB</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">内存即可流畅运行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">HY-MT1.5-7B模型是此前获得WMT25比赛30个语种</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">翻译冠军模型</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的升级版，重点提升了翻译准确率，大幅减少了译文中夹带注释和语种混杂的情况，实用性进一步增加。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在部分用户实际使用场景下，混元翻译1.8B和7B两个尺寸模型同时使用，可以实现</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">端侧和云侧模型的协同部署</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，提升模型的效果的一致性和稳定性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">基准测试方面，在中外互译和英外互译测试集Flores200、WMT25以及民汉语言的测试集中，Tencent-HY-MT1.5-1.8B</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">全</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">面超越Qwen3-32B</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，与</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Qwen3-235B-A22B</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等大尺寸闭源模型成绩不相上下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，在处理效率上，与主流商用翻译模型API对比，HY-MT1.5-1.8B处理</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">50个</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">tokens的平均耗时只有</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">0.18秒</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，其他模型的时间在</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">0.4秒</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">左右。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术方面，HY-MT1.5-1.8B能够用小尺寸实现大尺寸模型的效果，得益于On-Policy Distillation（大尺寸模型蒸馏）策略的引入，HY-MT1.5-7B作为Teacher，能够实时引导1.8B的Student模型，让其避免死记硬背标准答案，通过纠正在预测序列分布时的偏移，让小模型从错误中学习，进而提升能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.21\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f4e5849e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRw1TuyQQeiboSmMKMUM1Y6B4YCV2hwAl2A0Ikd75sHuDFYfNjypquEHyQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲On-Policy Distillation（大尺寸模型蒸馏）策略（来源：腾讯混元）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前两个模型均已在腾讯混元官网上线，在GitHub和Hugging Face等开源社区也可直接下载使用，Arm、高通、Intel、沐曦等多个平台均支持部署。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">混元官网：</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://hunyuan.tencent.com/modelSquare/home/list\" target=\"_blank\">https://hunyuan.tencent.com/modelSquare/home/list</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">GitHub链接：</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/HY-MT\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/HY-MT</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Hugging Face链接：</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/tencent/hy-mt15\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/collections/tencent/hy-mt15</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">互译成绩超越Qwen3-32B</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">响应速度仅0.18秒</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在常用的中外互译和英外互译测试集Flores200、WMT25以及民汉语言的测试集中，Tencent-HY-MT1.5-1.8B</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">全面超越Qwen3-32B</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等中等尺寸开源模型和</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">主流商用翻译API</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\">，达到</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Qwen3-235B-A22B</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等大尺寸闭源模型的</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">90分位</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.746\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed536976&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRwRxTj7VpsHDd89lvs4LBMYAL7Xh23YeLuEuLWeAGMXsCbupX6S5qzXg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲Flores200、WMT25以及民汉语言的测试集成绩（来源：腾讯混元）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在翻译质量与响应效率上，HY-MT1.5-1.8B模型在FLORES-200质量评估中取得了约</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">78%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的分数，同时平均响应时间仅为</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">0.18秒</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，超越主流商用翻译API。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.719\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef2bd565&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRwzvwJLvz87bYoZianpTUgc57ZUGwwvVkXicyuiabmic7KVuHeNzobv4A2bw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲FLORES-200质量评估成绩（来源：腾讯混元）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从术语到上下文翻译</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">腾讯混元翻译模型1.5</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">反应迅捷、准确率“能打”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">凭借优化的模型设计和推理逻辑，腾讯混元翻译模型1.5适用于</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">即时通讯、智能客服、移动翻译应用</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">高吞吐、实时翻译场景</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先是术语，腾讯混元翻译模型1.5具备</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">术语库自定义能力</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，用户可针对不同行业与专业场景（如医学、法律、金融、科技等）提前构建专属术语对照表，确保关键术语在翻译中保持</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">高度一致与准确性</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一功能有效弥补了小尺寸模型在</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">处理专业领域文本</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">时的词汇短板，使其在保障轻量化部署的同时，也能胜任高要求的行业翻译任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户可通过简单配置导入术语库，模型将在翻译过程中</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">优先采纳</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">用户定义的标准术语，从而提升专业文档、技术手册、合同文本等内容翻译的可靠性与权威性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 15px 8px 25px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1em; text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;visibility: visible; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">▲术语翻译（来源：腾讯混元）</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">智东西也上手尝试了一下，我们上传了一系列医学术语，让其翻译成中文。在反应速度上，腾讯混元翻译模型1.5就很快输出了翻译结果，几乎没有反应时间。与原文对照看，其翻译的成果准确度为</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">100%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4b7a622&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRwa3Ma5jNJWUxpTPOxpKh9aic1j7wVp6Tf9sQJDZ2llqjMB7EFnQ9Xy0w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲术语翻译（来源：智东西实测）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了英语外，我们还上传了5句职场中高频出现的粤语对话，看看腾讯混元翻译模型1.5的方言翻译效果如何。结果显示，腾讯混元翻译模型1.5也可以很准确地翻译出粤语用词和语气，准确度同样“能打”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ec96eda&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRwia9aLAZ3MB1RJzXDa584wsrFib2uMyN2RMG6iaszu4kT1u24k3caJ0LFA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲粤语翻译（来源：智东西实测）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其次是上下文翻译能力。该能力适用于实时对话翻译、长篇文献翻译及多轮交互场景。混元翻译模型模型具备较好的长文本与对话上下文理解能力，可基于前文语境持续优化后续翻译结果，显著提升长对话、多轮问答、连续段落等场景下的翻译连贯性与一致性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论是会议记录、访谈内容、小说章节还是技术文档的长篇翻译，模型均能有效捕捉并保持上下文逻辑关系，避免出现指代不清、语义断裂或风格不统一的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">▲上下文翻译（来源：腾讯混元）</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三是，带格式翻译能力，通过精准的指令遵循能力，混元翻译模型得以保持翻译前后的格式信息不变，让翻译结果更加准确实用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 15px 8px 25px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1em; text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;visibility: visible; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">▲带格式翻译（来源：腾讯混元）</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了直观展示混元Tencent-HY-MT1.5-1.8B的翻译效果，下面展示了与苹果手机自带离线翻译的结果对比：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.593\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5028732&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgatzElYQkXPQVCTruTkFRwVXcJlkpPMticibvA5LRCKeToibPhWzwakhoUmkyoUW19iaBb8nVx2qSOCw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲与苹果自带翻译对比（来源：腾讯混元）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：腾讯开源降低了翻译模型应用门槛</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">腾讯此次开源的小尺寸翻译模型，降低了翻译模型在手机等终端上运行的门槛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">腾讯混元翻译模型此前不仅在国际机器翻译比赛拿下30个第1名，也在首次开源一周内便登上Hugging Face模型趋势榜第一位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">混元翻译模型已经在腾讯内部多个业务场景落地应用，包括腾讯会议、企业微信、QQ浏览器、客服翻译等。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯混元开源 1.8B 翻译模型，支持 33 种语种 5 种方言，可在 1GB 内存手机上离线运行，性能媲美大型闭源模型，并通过 On-Policy Distillation 策略实现小尺寸高精度。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯混元开源 1.8B 翻译模型，支持 33 种语种 5 种方言，可在 1GB 内存手机上离线运行，性能媲美大型闭源模型，并通过 On-Policy Distillation 策略实现小尺寸高精度。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了腾讯混元开源的翻译模型 1.5 版本，包括 HY-MT1.5-1.8B 和 HY-MT1.5-7B 两款模型。其中 1.8B 模型专注于移动端和离线翻译场景，仅需 1GB 内存即可运行，并支持 33 种语种及 5 种方言互译。该模型在基准测试中表现卓越，超越了 Qwen3-32B，并与 Qwen3-235B-A22B 等大型闭源模型性能相当。其出色表现得益于引入 On-Policy Distillation 策略，通过大尺寸 Teacher 模型引导小尺寸 Student 模型学习。此外，文章强调了模型在术语库自定义、上下文理解和格式保持方面的优势，使其能够应对高吞吐、实时翻译场景，并在医学术语和粤语方言翻译中展现出高准确率。腾讯此次开源降低了翻译模型在终端应用上的门槛，目前已在 Hugging Face 和 GitHub 开源。",
